<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Infrastructure R√©seau - Monitoring Temps R√©el</title>
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="60">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.8em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .stats-overview {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .stat-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            border-left: 5px solid;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .stat-card.total { border-left-color: #3498db; }
        .stat-card.online { border-left-color: #27ae60; }
        .stat-card.offline { border-left-color: #e74c3c; }
        .stat-card.ping { border-left-color: #f39c12; }
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2.8em;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 1em;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .devices-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            max-width: 1600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .device-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-left: 6px solid;
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
        }
        .device-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .device-card.operational { border-left-color: #27ae60; }
        .device-card.warning { border-left-color: #f39c12; }
        .device-card.error { border-left-color: #e74c3c; }
        .device-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .device-icon {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        .device-status {
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .status-operational { background: #27ae60; }
        .status-warning { background: #f39c12; }
        .status-error { background: #e74c3c; }
        .device-name {
            font-size: 1.6em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .device-location {
            color: #bdc3c7;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        .device-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .detail-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .detail-value {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            opacity: 0.8;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .technical-info {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .tech-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #3498db;
        }
        .tech-list {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .tech-item {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            padding: 5px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            opacity: 0.8;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        .access-btn {
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 15px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .access-btn:hover {
            background: #2980b9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üåê Infrastructure R√©seau Temps R√©el</h1>
        <p>Monitoring des √©quipements WiFi, routeurs et points d'acc√®s - <%= lastUpdate %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-overview">
        <div class="stat-card total">
            <span class="stat-number"><%= stats.total_devices %></span>
            <span class="stat-label">üìä √âquipements R√©seau</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card online">
            <span class="stat-number"><%= stats.online %></span>
            <span class="stat-label">üü¢ Op√©rationnels</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card offline">
            <span class="stat-number"><%= stats.offline %></span>
            <span class="stat-label">üî¥ Hors Service</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card ping">
            <span class="stat-number"><%= stats.avg_response_time %>ms</span>
            <span class="stat-label">‚ö° Latence Moyenne</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="devices-grid">
        <% Object.values(devices).forEach(device => { %>
            <div class="device-card <%= device.status %>">
                <div class="device-header">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
                        <span class="device-icon"><%= device.icon %></span>
                        <div>
                            <div class="device-name"><%= device.name %></div>
                            <div class="device-location">üìç <%= device.location %></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="device-status status-<%= device.status %>">
                        <%= device.status === 'operational' ? 'üü¢ OP√âRATIONNEL' : 
                            device.status === 'warning' ? 'üü° ATTENTION' : 'üî¥ ERREUR' %>
                    </span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="device-details">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-value"><%= device.ip %></div>
                        <div class="detail-label">üåê Adresse IP</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-value"><%= device.responseTime %>ms</div>
                        <div class="detail-label">üì° Latence</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-value"><%= device.protocol.toUpperCase() %></div>
                        <div class="detail-label">üîí Protocole</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <% if (device.model) { %>
                        <div class="detail-item">
                            <div class="detail-value"><%= device.model %></div>
                            <div class="detail-label">üè∑Ô∏è Mod√®le</div>
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>

                <% if (device.wifi_info || device.system_info || device.network_services) { %>
                    <div class="technical-info">
                        <div class="tech-title">üîß Informations Techniques</div>
                        <div class="tech-list">
                            <% if (device.wifi_info) { %>
                                <% if (device.wifi_info.channel) { %>
                                    <div class="tech-item">                                    <div class="tech-item">üì° SSID 2.4GHz: <%= device.wifi_info.ssid %></div>
                                    <div class="tech-item">üì° SSID 5GHz: <%= device.wifi_info.ssid5g || "N/A" %></div>
                                    üì∂ Canal WiFi: <%= device.wifi_info.channel %></div>
                                <% } %>
                                <% if (device.wifi_info.mode) { %>
                                    <div class="tech-item">üì° Mode: <%= device.wifi_info.mode %></div>
                                <% } %>
                                <% if (device.wifi_info.bands) { %>
                                    <div class="tech-item">üåê Bandes: <%= device.wifi_info.bands.join(', ') %></div>
                                <% } %>
                            <% } %>
                            
                            <% if (device.system_info) { %>
                                <% if (device.system_info.firmware) { %>
                                    <div class="tech-item">üíæ Firmware: <%= device.system_info.firmware %></div>
                                <% } %>
                                <% if (device.system_info.uptime) { %>
                                    <div class="tech-item">‚è±Ô∏è Uptime: <%= device.system_info.uptime %></div>
                                <% } %>
                            <% } %>
                            
                            <% if (device.network_services && device.network_services.estimated_clients) { %>
                                <div class="tech-item">üë• Clients: ~<%= device.network_services.estimated_clients %></div>
                            <% } %>
                            
                            <% if (device.enterprise_features) { %>
                                <div class="tech-item">üîê VPN: <%= device.enterprise_features.vpn_tunnels || 'N/A' %></div>
                                <div class="tech-item">üè¢ VLAN: <%= device.enterprise_features.vlan_support || 'N/A' %></div>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% } %>

                <% if (device.protocol && device.online) { %>
                    <div style="text-align: center;">
                        <a href="<%= device.protocol %>://<%= device.ip %>" target="_blank" class="access-btn">
                            üîó Acc√©der √† l'interface
                        </a>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        <% }); %>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>üîÑ Actualisation automatique toutes les 60 secondes | 
           <a href="/" style="color: white; text-decoration: none;">üè† Dashboard Principal</a> |
           Infrastructure r√©seau surveill√©e 24/7
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
